name: ZIM a photo series on mens mental health

metadata.name: ALIGN
metadata.description:
The depths of my heart has a treasure chest, unopened,
unseen by the depths of the heart of the ocean,
I redo, relook, realign my steps forward,
but the only way that appears is to move within...

I try, I fail, I move, I resign,
There's nothing more beautiful than this loop divine,
lessons, life, love lights my soul,
i am awakened to my deepest pore...

Talk, they said talk to someone, loud and clear,
yet the softest conversation with myself, worked,
I am here, I am alive, self belief is not linear,
it gave me purpose, and i am more than ready to conquer,
every fear...

- Ashwini Dodani
